{"tid":1773004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報—警批准民陣遊行顯示政府誠意","createTime":"2019-12-07T06:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T12:08:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"441a52e3872ecf85fdc376d6604cd6619201b770","tid":1773004,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"內地官方媒體《人民日報》發表文章，指香港反修例風波持續至今，不少遊行集會演變成嚴重暴力違法行為，更有人盜竊化學品升級暴行，近乎恐怖主義分子的行徑，強調暴力不應是香港的標籤。<br />\n<br />\n文章又稱，警方已向明日民陣舉辦的遊行發出不反對通知書，顯示特區政府尊重市民表達自由的誠意之舉，相信於「一國兩制」方針及《基本法》下，香港可讓修例風波在和平理性討論氛圍中降溫，找到解決當前問題的方法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2324456/人民日報%3A警批准民陣遊行顯示政府誠意\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2324456%2F%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%253A%E8%AD%A6%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%AA%A0%E6%84%8F&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=1dbd1cfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2324456/人民日報%3A警批准民陣遊行顯示政府誠意</a>"},{"pid":"cea2078e937a4f10386cefccd7fe65aa67afa0c7","tid":1773004,"uid":171399,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"其實唔駛咁辛苦搵咩解決方法啦 <br />\n落實五大訴求 暫時解決呢個危機"},{"pid":"d03e83cb72479544c7c1f5f35fe2ca6741ee3b59","tid":1773004,"uid":220182,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"遊行顯示民眾誠意"},{"pid":"a9d3916a6861935464bf0fbae11ec19ed1b90de7","tid":1773004,"uid":224066,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSRAKq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSRAKq6.jpg&h=6e7a3e91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5fad43f1a7986d4749f4d5c44c653ea71081c11a","tid":1773004,"uid":15084,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:31:07.000Z","msg":"准你老母個老母<br />\n屌你而家准